title: All in One SEO Pack Pro v2.3.7.2 - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
All in One SEO Pack Pro is the popular WordPress plugin for managing the Search Engine Optimization of your website or blog. All in One SEO Pack is the most downloaded plugin for WordPress with over 14 million downloads to date. Chances are you've searched Google and found a website that's running this powerful WordPress plugin. Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
